'''Mototakisiw''' (''mototaxis'')

Takisini ye sɔrɔ yirawasira dɔ ye [[Segu]] demisɛn dɔw fɛ wa a bɛ taama nɔgɔya. Bi, siniwa motow ye fan bɛɛ fa i n’a fɔ jakarita, yamaha ani suguya wɛrɛw. I n’a fɔ o se tɛ bɛɛ ye, dɔw diyagoyalen don ka bolimafɛn dɔw ta i n’a fɔ Takisini furancɛ surun dɔw la. O kɛra baara sira ye demisɛn dɔw bolo walasa k’u ka musakaw dakala. <ref>[http://fasokan.maneno.org/bam/articles/zxy1256677129/ Mototakisiw (Takisininw) ye sɔrɔ yirawasira dɔ ye Segu Mali la.]</ref>

